"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ebe054d7d661fc7d6ca11ccef5697361f453a63","tid":2104280,"uid":35505,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"33ab5d84b54dabdb9f72930299bd04aa9e96e3cb","tid":2104280,"uid":171107,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T23:04:03.000Z","msg":"5.1級都上新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好心10級先報出來啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T23:51:45.000Z","msg":"5月26日北京3.6級地震<br />\n7月12日唐山5.1級地震<br />\n睇怕都係前震，主震未到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c04b8e9637d4048f77d65afdb92f64752d02145","tid":2104280,"uid":35505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T23:56:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1537248-20200712.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1537248-20200712.htm&d=GdzNT1%2FdEV%2FiwqmWSoLNnjsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=09af9d54\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1537248-20200712.htm&h=a81914ef\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1537248-20200712.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n河北唐山古冶區發生5.1級地震　天津北京震感明顯<br />\n<br />\n中國地震台網錄得在河北唐山市古冶區，在早上6時38分，發生5.1級地震，震源深度10公里，天津市距離震央132公里。<br />\n<br />\n內地民眾表示，天津及北京都有震感，居民家中吊燈搖晃明顯。<br />\n<br />\n大約半小時後，在接近同一地區，發生2.2級地震，震源深度15公里。<br />\n<br />\n根據中國地震台網的數據顯示，震央周邊200公里內近5年來發生3級以上地震共有17次，今次的地震屬最大震級。"},{"pid":"2c31696e8f501d11b75684da71a44949342cf35b","tid":2104280,"uid":35505,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T23:57:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1537249-20200712.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1537249-20200712.htm&d=GdzNT1%2FdEV%2FiwqmWSoLNnjsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=bfb47d24\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1537249-20200712.htm&h=2fbfdfac\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1537249-20200712.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n河北唐山古冶區5.1級地震　北京鐵路部列車停駛檢查<br />\n<br />\n中國地震台網錄得在河北唐山市古冶區，在早上6時38分，發生5.1級地震，震源深度10公里，天津市距離震央132公里，之後一個小時內，至少發生兩次強度達2級的地震。<br />\n<br />\n內地民眾表示，天津及北京都有震感，居民家中吊燈搖晃明顯。北京鐵路部門立即啟動應急預案，暫停途經該地區的旅客列車，全面檢查鐵路設備設施，以確保旅客列車運行安全。<br />\n<br />\n根據中國地震台網的數據顯示，震央周邊200公里內近5年來發生3級以上地震共有17次，今次的地震屬最大震級。"},{"pid":"1854583cace371984ffb02fe8ec9c64890cf54bb","tid":2104280,"uid":78546,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"d40f27559b71516d4bd1d4569a7c16809f6cf346","tid":2104280,"uid":34652,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T23:11:12.000Z","msg":"1976年嗰次仲勁啦<br />\n5.1級唔會嚇怕中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T23:59:22.000Z","msg":"N年前睇本書<br />\n都係話一開始弱震 冇人理<br />\n跟住....<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55cc56547aca581ee3e0bfd6b6001747cf37a699","tid":2104280,"uid":41308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T00:00:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50b1e392c20b1512b3b12746c3d65cd9d1422fc0","tid":2104280,"uid":59511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T00:01:56.000Z","msg":"冇7～8級就唔洗報啦，空歡喜咗半秒"},{"pid":"4f48beee45411a38326665b494ee4c590fe04ef9","tid":2104280,"uid":16818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"332db97ba62c1fd026f3392fc501d6e9340cb56e","tid":2104280,"uid":